                "title": "A Hardy\u2013Ramanujan\u2013Rademacher-type formula for (r,s)-regular partitions",
                "year": 2012,
                "venue": "",
                "citation_count": 11,
                "reference_count": 33,
                "abstract": "Let pr,s(n) denote the number of partitions of a positive integer n into parts containing no multiples of r or s, where r>1 and s>1 are square-free, relatively prime integers. We use classical methods to derive a Hardy\u2013Ramanujan\u2013Rademacher-type infinite series for pr,s(n).",
